    "title": "#357.乔布斯：创造非凡，活出自我——《Make Something Wonderful》解读",
    "author": "跨国串门儿计划",
    "date": "2025.12.31",
    "coverUrl": "https://image.xyzcdn.net/FgPi3C76e0yvQlUYo8TDbk1GTgp8.png",
